name: Skechers Women Your Black Slippers
description:
Stylish and uber cool, these Tone-Ups flip flops from skechers add an extra bounce to your step. With a simple strappy design, these slippers are designed to activate your calf, thigh and buttock muscles. Look super stylish in these comfortable slippers all day long.

Upper
Synthetic straps on the forefoot and midfoot with a velvetty upper and padded fabric inner for abrasion-free comfort and style
Midfoot strap has a buckle closure to offer a customised Fit
Padded PU footbed for cushioned comfort
Soft PU heel pad for comfort

Outsole
Durable rubber outsole designed to create instability with every step and therefore activate underused muscles to maintain balance
Balance pods that create slight and constant shifts in weight to offer a more intense workout with lesser stress

shoe care
Wipe surface with soft, clean, dry cloth to remove dust
Do not wash or store in direct sunlight

Do not wash or store in direct sunlight

name: Skechers Women Shape-Ups White Shoe
description:
Run less, get more with the skechers Resistance Runner shoes. Fab to look and a great gift for the feet, this pair of running shoes is designed with the best of technologies to offer the best comfort and health quicker. The Resamax kinetic wedge technology helps create a more fluid stride and helps reduce injuries and enhance performance.

skechers promises that running with the Resistance Runners helps activate postural muscles by upto 85%, activate gluteus medius muscles by upto 71%, calf muscles upto 68% and burn 13.2% more calories than other running shoes. What's better, this shoe comes with an additional pair of laces in a different colour to suit your style.

So jet set, pick up your pair and burn away those calories with ease!

name: Puma Men Evo Casual Shoes
description:

Padded collar and tongue for enhanced comfort and a snug Fit
Perforations on toe and midfoot for enhanced ventilation

High ankle support for comfort
Branding tag on tongue, printing on ankle and back heel

TPU and EVA midsole combined to offer support and ample cushioning
